title: Saturday (group)
text:
Saturday (세러데이) is a South Korean girl group formed by SD Entertainment in 2018. The group debuted on July 18, 2018, with MMook JJi BBa., the group currently consists of Juyeon, Yuki, Ayeon and Minseo. In 2022, the building of SD Entertainment shut down, and in 2023 the group moved to Yoonso Group.
